    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car for me and is still in great shape, running smoothly and looking sharp! It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle that\u2019s been well-cared for without paying those sky-high new car prices. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and I\u2019m sure you will too. Drop me a message if you\u2019d like to come see it!",
      "price": 29800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
