    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension remains tight, utilizing its original MacPherson strut/multi-link geometry to provide the balanced handling characteristics this chassis is renowned for. While the aesthetic reflects its service as a spirited grand tourer, the mechanical vitals are robust and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
